	ng upcoming dates: \\n\\nFebruary 15th\\nMarch 15th\\nApril 19th\\nMay 17t
	h\\nJune 21st\\nJuly 19th (37th Annual Indian Days Powwow Weekend\\\, star
	ting at 9:00 AM)\\n\\nTiming and Location Details \\n\\nStart Time: 10:00 
